<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unpaid" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unpaid,</orth> not paid: <cit><quote>there remains u. a hundred thousand more,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 2.134" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 134</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>rustling in u. for silk,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 24</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>she should that duty leave u. to you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.48" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 48</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the worth thou art u. for,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.307" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 307</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>